Smuxi is in [AUR][], so just download the PKGBUILD and run makepkg.
Alternatively if you're using yaourt just run the following command:

    sudo yaourt -S smuxi

Now you can start Smuxi from the GNOME or KDE menu.

  [AUR]: http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=19247
